== About me
I am currently a PhD student in [http://cse.zju.edu.cn/ Colledge of Control Science and Engineering] at [https://www.zju.edu.cn/ Zhejiang University (ZJU)], fortunately advised by [https://person.zju.edu.cn/en/jmchen Prof. Jiming Chen] and [https://person.zju.edu.cn/en/cp Prof. Peng Cheng]. I also received the B.S. degrees [http://cse.zju.edu.cn/ Colledge of Control Science and Engineering] from [https://www.zju.edu.cn/ Zhejiang University (ZJU)] in 2020.  

== Research
My research interests include 
- Robust Decision-Making
- Multi-Agent Reinforcement Learning
- Population Games and Evolutionary Dynamics
- Trust and Reputation Mechanism Design

